<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Scrabble Tile Bag Distribution — All 100 Tiles Listed</h1>

<p>A standard Scrabble game contains exactly 100 tiles — 98 letter tiles and 2 blanks. Understanding the distribution is fundamental to strategic play. Knowing how many of each letter exist helps you track what's been played, predict opponent racks, and make smarter decisions about tile management.</p>

